{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act18d3", "eventName": "覆潮之下", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SV-1", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "闖入者", "storyInfo": "深夜，斯卡蒂發現醫療艙裡的幽靈鯊失蹤，而擄走她的正是幽靈鯊以前的隊長歌蕾蒂婭。臨走之前，歌蕾蒂婭告訴斯卡蒂，接下來她們將前往一座伊比利亞小城。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沉默。怪異。捉摸不定。外鄉人。"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們自然會這麼說。"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陰暗。冷血。見死不救。天生怪物。"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有人在背後都會這麼說。"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人只要失去了故鄉，就什麼都不是了。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "照理來說，來到這裡的我，應該能開始一個新的生活。"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，過往揮之不去。這些東西會順著影子爬上你的小腿，把你向泥沼深處拽去。"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們誰都擺脫不了過往。"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果有一天，你的故鄉找上了你......"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_corridor"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$farce_intro", "key": "$farce_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "2:33 A.M. 天氣/陰"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅德島本艦，走廊"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好啦！等這份報告提交完成，你的外勤任務就算結束了。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等一下，又是......空白？咳，咳咳......", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從頭到尾，只有“完成”兩個字啊！", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "任務確實完成了。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是、是這樣沒錯......", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你多寫兩句話也不會有什麼問題吧？！", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（怎麼辦......比想像的還難對付？）", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（之前沒和她說過什麼話，這回說是要和她對接，雖然組長提醒過......但果然還是很難辦。）", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（深呼吸）", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好、好的，我明白了。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "關於任務中的細節，如果博士有疑問，會再找你確認。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......博士？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#5"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，凱爾希醫生說你也許不會想向她提交報告......她還說阿米婭對你太溫柔了，這樣下去是不行的......之類。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後就把這次任務歸檔到博士那邊了。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個女人，哼。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你想直接向博士面呈報告嗎？現在博士好像不在，你可以休息幾天，等博士回來。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在你提交的這份報告，真的很需要再補充！", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#5"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很麻煩。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#5"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，任務編碼F1071，確認提交，後續補充——", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦？", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把檔案還給我。我想起來，再完善點內容也可以。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊！當然可以！那就麻煩你啦。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（比預想的要順利一些啊......）", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣的話，我這邊沒什麼事了，還請回去好好休......嗯？", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#8"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#8", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的臉色一下子就變了，發生什麼了？", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可能是。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#8"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#8", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？在這裡？船上嗎？難道是入侵者？！聽人說你五感特別敏銳，難道是......", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不對啊，如果船上有危險，警報會響起來吧？", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......歌聲。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#8"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#8", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歌？什麼歌？呃，很安靜啊，我沒聽見......", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡，為什麼會有歌聲？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#8"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#8", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實好像有些嗡嗡聲，但那也不是歌吧？羅德島上的各類儀器都還在運轉，有可能是，是機械振動？你還不習慣嗎？", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic", "name2": "char_263_skadi#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，氣味。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#8"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海水的味道。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#8"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......斯卡蒂？你有點嚇到我了。你在說什......", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦？喂！斯卡蒂！", "name": "羅德島幹員"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯卡蒂跑得太急、太快，她跑進樓梯通道，她害怕乘電梯幾秒間的焦慮就會讓那氣味溜走。"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "一個獵人走上海岸♪", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她能聽到這歌。這艘船上的大多數人，他們聽不見。"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種語言，這種旋律，喚起了她的回憶。她不是個戀舊的人，但她太熟悉了。"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但......不該這樣。這首歌不該出現在這裡。"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "他的家鄉在後，徒餘哀歎♪", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歌聲在這艘船的管道裡遊移。"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海水的氣味從艙壁裡不斷滲出來。"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯卡蒂也同樣記得這味道。潮濕逼近了她，她的皮膚不住地收縮、繃緊。緊張，卻也是激動。"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道她醒了？她不禁加快了腳步。"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幽靈鯊！", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#8"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ri_1"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_dooropen"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她拉開醫療艙的門。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "床鋪是空的。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#8"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "也有可能是清醒了以後想出去走走吧。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等......這是什麼？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她撿起那個東西，捏了捏。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......好像是她的東西。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "幽靈鯊的金鏈被隨便地丟在地上。或許是故意的。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她很討厭這東西嗎？那她肯定是不喜歡現在自己的身份了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "教會，至少海裡教會的所有事，都不是好事。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但......不對勁。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "外人。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "不知為什麼，斯卡蒂突然想起了這個詞。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她意識到那其實不是幽靈鯊的氣味。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "比起以前的幽靈鯊，現在這氣味太濃烈，又太冷酷。斯卡蒂懷疑自己只是被驚喜沖昏了頭腦。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就在這附近。你是誰？出來。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "是深海獵人。但不是幽靈鯊。竟然還有其他活下來的深海獵人！", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但為什麼在這裡？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "......幽靈鯊去哪了？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......無論你是誰或者你是什麼。出來。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她得去追。有什麼不對勁。她感到對方的確在附近。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_corridor"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "斯卡蒂衝出房門，一個身影在走廊深處一閃而過。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "不......有兩個人。歌聲仍在，對方仍在低吟。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "幽靈鯊。那個深海獵人帶走了幽靈鯊。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "blackstart": 0.3, "blackend": 0.5}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真慢。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再不過來，我們可就要走了。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#5"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "獵人！你是誰？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#5"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯卡蒂一躍，轉過角落，她不自主地摸索起身上能用的武器。"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#5"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——你在做什麼？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#5"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那一刻她竟先直視了對方的雙眼。"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#5"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......等等，你是......", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#5"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個自己沒有想過的人。"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "ac18_01", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "blackstart": 0.3, "blackend": 0.5}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯卡蒂。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "氣色不錯。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#5"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你......難道是二大隊的，幽靈鯊的隊長......？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#5"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是......歌蕾蒂婭......？！", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#5"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有些時日了，斯卡蒂。你還能記起阿戈爾的歌，我很欣慰。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "斯卡蒂沒能從她的表情裡摳出哪怕一絲絲的“欣慰”。這個女人，從自己知道她開始，表情就從來沒變過。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "高挑的女性抱著幽靈鯊。數年來，斯卡蒂唯一知曉還存活的深海獵人，幽靈鯊，現在正靠在歌蕾蒂婭的肩上，做著又一場難得平靜的夢。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "在幽靈鯊的隊長吐出第一個詞的同時，歌聲消失了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "斯卡蒂一陣恍惚。從舷窗湧入、獨屬陸地的乾燥的風拂過斯卡蒂略顯乾燥的面頰，她心想，這個獵人還活著，歌蕾蒂婭活著。斯卡蒂終於又找到了一個同類。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "不對。是歌蕾蒂婭找到了她們。只是......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我以為你死了。你們拼死讓我們過去的。我以為你們全死了。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "生命可貴。很高興看到你也活著。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然幽靈鯊還活著，我也常在想，你們二隊是不是還能有其他人活下來......", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是怎麼找到這裡的？幽靈鯊......她還是待在病房比較好。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯卡蒂印象裡最嚴厲的獵人之一，在這時選擇了一言不發。"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "懷疑在斯卡蒂心裡滋生。"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她變了很多。她現在未必認識你，她的身體也還很虛弱。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "虛弱？獵人不會虛弱。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你來陸地上多久了？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "地上的病，特殊的病，在掏空她的身體。這艘船上的人能穩定她的病情。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些年過來，她從來沒清醒過。現在的幽靈鯊是另外一個人。我不知道是什麼把她變成了這樣。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歌蕾蒂婭沒說話，微風吹過，歌蕾蒂婭的髮絲隨之飄蕩，掩住了她的眼神。"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯卡蒂意識到了問題所在。"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......歌蕾蒂婭。你就是歌蕾蒂婭，我不會認錯人。但你要做什麼？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想帶她去哪？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為獵人在陸地上是自由的。我是不是理解錯了什麼？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，歌蕾蒂婭......她還睡著。她想不想走，你沒問過她。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想從這帶走她。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的這些新同僚，你似乎對他們青睞有加。他們對你是否也一樣？你隨手就能捏碎他們的脊樑，又怎麼能不讓他們感到恐懼？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陸地上的這些人對我們有敵意也正常，但這艘船上的不會。我遇到的不會。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還沒能理解你放鬆警惕的原因。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不......這件事我不想他們摻和，問題也不在我身上，不在他們身上。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "問題在你。"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯卡蒂往前走了一步。"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這麼做是什麼意思，你最好說明清楚。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "獵人斯卡蒂。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——在陸地上我不用執政官的身份約束你。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔......", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我也沒有義務向你坦白。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是認為，我應該讓你知道，是我帶走了她，我自己的隊員。這就足夠。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今晚的你還不需要知道原因。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是幽靈鯊她！", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——（伊比利亞語）——", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown3"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "在那個名字完整地傳到斯卡蒂耳朵裡之前，歌蕾蒂婭就已自舷窗滑進了艦外的月色，幽靈鯊癱軟的身體也隨之一起消失了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "斯卡蒂沒有伸手去抓，她動都沒動。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她清楚，歌蕾蒂婭想跑，自己是怎麼都追不上的；但如果歌蕾蒂婭只是想跑，那就不會給自己留下訊息。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她在求助，或者她在誘騙自己。斯卡蒂將信將疑，又別無他法。至少她沒命令自己去做什麼，別去做什麼。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“鹽風城。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "歌蕾蒂婭是這麼說的。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "斯卡蒂她不得不去。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鹽風城。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這重逢也太不感人了。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_desert_1"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$farce_intro", "key": "$farce_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你們在這幹什麼？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007", "name2": "avg_npc_008", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，她是斯卡蒂吧？", "name": "賞金獵人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007", "name2": "avg_npc_008", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是覺得她有點眼熟。和畫像有點像。", "name": "賞金獵人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007", "name2": "avg_npc_008", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......啊！哈哈，得來全不費工夫啊......", "name": "賞金獵人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是斯卡蒂沒錯，我們蹲對地方了。", "name": "賞金獵人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#5"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#5"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007", "name2": "avg_npc_008", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，她真應了......而且你看她那把劍。她真的是斯卡蒂！", "name": "賞金獵人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007", "name2": "avg_npc_008", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯卡蒂，你還記得“上尉”嗎？我們拿了他的錢，要給他報仇，要你的命！", "name": "賞金獵人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007", "name2": "avg_npc_008", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你頭殼壞了......你頭殼壞了！我就說這是個餿主意！", "name": "賞金獵人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們不是說拿了他的錢騙騙人就好嗎？！什麼報仇啊，什麼拿懸賞啊，怎麼可能！", "name": "賞金獵人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想想那些傳聞！真要是她，這趟活我們還能賺到錢嗎？命都要賠上！", "name": "賞金獵人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看我們還是趁早散了吧！拿上你的破銅爛鐵逃吧！", "name": "賞金獵人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007", "name2": "avg_npc_008", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呸。", "name": "賞金獵人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你自己爬回到你的爛床上抱著馱獸的尿喊媽媽去吧。一個長頭髮的年輕姑娘就讓你嚇破了膽。想讓老子無功而返，沒門！", "name": "賞金獵人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008", "name2": "avg_npc_008", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說得對！就算她真的是斯卡蒂，就算斯卡蒂再怎麼厲害，那她現在也只有一個人對不對？", "name": "賞金獵人C"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們有一、二......呃，好多個！", "name": "賞金獵人C"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008", "name2": "avg_npc_008", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是那些厲害的賞金獵人不都爛在了地裡？那時候，她也是一個人！", "name": "賞金獵人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你再想想，你每次說自己人多的時候，真的會有好事？", "name": "賞金獵人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有誰看見了？要我說，那幾個傢伙，說不定是夜裡喝醉了進了同一個漂亮庫蘭塔的屋裡。", "name": "賞金獵人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結果人家從褲襠裡掏出弩來一陣亂射，把大家的腦袋都給轟爛了。", "name": "賞金獵人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傳聞就是那麼回事，要是不誇大些，那些抱著琴唱歌的，那什麼吟遊歌手，他們還能有飯吃？", "name": "賞金獵人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼一劍能劈開五十座山啊......老子還能一拳頭打穿倫蒂尼姆呢！", "name": "賞金獵人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽我說兄弟們！想吃飯的就跟我一塊上！", "name": "賞金獵人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "管她斯卡蒂活卡蒂的，我們在這把她弄死，之後不怕人搶金子！加上其他人懸賞她腦袋的錢，下半輩子根本不用愁！", "name": "賞金獵人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#8"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "給你們個機會。現在跑還來得及，我沒時間和你們折騰。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#8"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008", "name2": "avg_npc_008", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$chasing_intro", "key": "$chasing_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上啊！宰了她！", "name": "賞金獵人C"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#8"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#8"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（阿戈爾語）爛掉的海草最黏人。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#8"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒想到，不會變的就只有劣質賞金獵人的愚蠢。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#8"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}